The legend returns—Ragnarok Ascended has officially landed in ARK: Survival Ascended!

This massive 144km² map has been fully rebuilt with stunning biomes, unforgettable landmarks, and brand-new secrets. Brave Murder Murder Snow, explore lush new islands, and take on the deadly Ice Wyvern to unlock powerful Tek gear.

Discover ancient ruins, dive through underwater labyrinths, and ride into battle on the mighty Bison in this wild, myth-forged world. Whether you're returning or exploring for the first time—this is your saga to shape.

Ragnarok Ascended is available now as a free DLC for all ARK: Survival Ascended players.

Forge your legend. The saga continues.
